libcfg+: libcfg+ (Command line and configuration file parsing library)
libcfg+:
libcfg+: libcfg+ is a C library that features multi- command line and
libcfg+: configuration file parsing. It is possible to set up various special
libcfg+: properties such as quoting characters, deliminator strings, file
libcfg+: comment prefixes, multi-line postfixes, and more. It supports many
libcfg+: data types such as booleans, integers, decimal numbers, strings with
libcfg+: many additional data type flags (such as multiple values for a single
libcfg+: option).
libcfg+: http://platon.sk/projects/main_page.php?project_id=3
